### Kuyruga katil (kapasite dolu senaryosu)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queue/{{eventId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Pozisyon sorgula
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queue/{{eventId}}/position
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Ikinci kullanici katilir
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queue/{{eventId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Kuyruktan cik
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queue/{{eventId}}/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
